data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home nestled in a cul-de-sac within a sought after neighborhood. Immerse yourself in the spaciousness and comfort this home offers. The main level boasts beautiful LVP (Luxury Vinyl Plank) floors that add a touch of elegance to the living spaces. Stay comfortable year-round with the brand new HVAC system, delivering efficient heating and cooling. Plus, the added convenience of a portable generator hook up provides peace of mind during power outages. With its generous layout and prime location, this home is perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this exceptional property your own.
